Key Match Events: Jamal Musiala scored once and set up three more goals as Germany crushed Hungary 5-0.
Niclas Füllkrug scored the opening goal for Germany.
Kai Havertz scored a penalty in the 81st minute.
Miscellaneous Highlights: Germany's Jamal Musiala was a standout performer with one goal and three assists.
The match took place at Merkur Spiel-Arena in Düsseldorf, Germany, with an attendance of 49,235.
